Package org.hibernate.query.sqm.mutation.internal.idtable

Support for multi-table SQM mutation (insert, update, delete) operations using a table to temporarily hold the matching ids. There are 3 forms: * LocalTemporaryTableStrategy uses local temp tables as defined by the SQL spec * GlobalTemporaryTableStrategy uses global temp tables as defined by the SQL spec * PersistentTableStrategy uses normal table managed by Hibernate.
